  Locus:
    Page: 120
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Ego/Vanity
---
The ego is really our weakness, the way our disbelief in ourselves shows in
life. When we give up fighting for it and determine to discipline it, we are
on our way toward being ourselves and mature individuals.
